{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schihs Leetas tew taps darritas/ tapehz ka tu teem Pa- ganeem eſſi pakkat maukojuſi/ un ar winnu Suhdu-Deeweem ſagahniuſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Us tawas Mahtas Zelfu eſſi tu statgajſti/ tapehz uodoh- ſchu es winnas Bifkeri tawa Rohkâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta fakka tas Klungs KUNGS: Tew irr tas Bifke- ris tawas Mahtas jadserx / kâ dsiffch un plats tas irr / kur daundstelp eekſcha/ tu tapſi par Aptmeekli un Mehdifchannu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu peedserfces no ſtipra Dſehreena/ un Skunnibas/ tas Bifkeris tawas Mahtas Sama- rijas irr weens Bifkeris tahs Nopohſtſchanaſs un Noskum- ſchanaſs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu dserſi un iſtaisifi winau/ un fatreehti winna Gab- balus/ un ſaplohfſti tawas Kruh- tis/ jo es eſmu to runnajs/ fak- ka tas Klungs KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz ta fakka tas Klungs KUNGS: Tadeht ka tu mannts eſſi atsmirfuſi / un mannis ais tawu Mugguru met- tuſi/ tad ir tu neſs tawu Kannu Leetu un tawas Maukoſchanaſs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija us man: Tu Zilweka Behrns/ ne gribbi tu Aälu un Aälibu fohtiſt/ un winnahm tawas Negantibas ſtahſtiht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tahs irru to Laulibu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wehl wairak irr tahs man ſcho darrijutchas/ tahs irr to Brihdimannas twehtas Wee- tas neschkiſtas darriſchas / un mannas Swehdeenas ſagahniſ- chas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo kad tahs ſawus Behr- nus ſaweem Suhdu-Deeweem bij nokawufchas/ tad nahze tahs tai paſchâ Deena us mannu ſwehtu Weetu to ſagahniht/ un redſi/ ta irr tahs darriſchas man- na Naimma Widdii.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tahs irr arri pehz Wih- reem fuhtiſchas / kam no tahte- nes bij janahk / us kurren kad weens Webſtneſſis tappe teh- tihts/ raugi / tad nahze tee / preekſch teem pascheem tu mas- gajees/ un darrijees tewi janſu/ un igresnojees ar Skaistumu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un fehdeji us weenu erahſchnu Gultu / preekſch ka ſtahweja weens fataſſihts Galds/ un us ka tu mannu Kwehpja- Sahſt un mannu Eſti bij zehluſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tur (zehlaſs) weena Balts fahdas preezigas Drau- dses/ un tahs fuhttja pehz teem Wihreem no tahs leelas Zilweſu Draudses/ un Sabeeri tappe no tahs Luksueſes atweiſti/ tee likke\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
